history.content:
TBP is hosting an infosession with General Motors!

📍 Location: 290 HMMB (Hearst Memorial Mining Building)
📆 Date & Time: Monday, 9/20, 6-7pm
🍕 Refreshments: Pizza will be offered outdoors after the event, but masks will be required indoors!


Explore job opportunities at General Motors at the infosession!
======
Event Info:
• Learn about full-time and internship openings
• Overview of the recruiting process
• "Day in the Life" - Wiliam Hotchkiss (Director, Energy Solutions @GM)
• Network with GM representatives

https://www.facebook.com/events/181685537319998/
